Package: ak
Title: Event-Study Designs for Discrete Outcomes via Transition Independence
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Young", "Ahn", , "youngahn@upenn.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements event-study designs for discrete outcomes using
    transition independence and latent group structure. Estimates treatment
    effects when outcomes are discrete and categorical, replacing the parallel
    trends assumption with transition independence. Accommodates unobserved
    heterogeneity via finite mixture models and a two-stage EM algorithm with
    bootstrap inference.
